## 8. Open Questions

- **Header-match search result UI** — search results are a flat list ranked by filename relevance first, then heading relevance (locked). For v1.0 MVP, heading-match results render as `<filename> · <heading text>` on a single line. Refinement (grouped under file? line context?) deferred to Iteration E.
- **Toolbar icon set** — the editor top toolbar contains the file-name label and a (disabled) view-mode segmented control stub in v1.0. Final icon complement (info, share, etc.) finalized in Iteration B alongside the rendering toggle that activates the segmented control.
- **App icon** — placeholder `Assets.xcassets/AppIcon.appiconset/` with empty slots. Real icon integrated in Iteration E.
